title: VALKYRIE DRIVE -BHIKKHUNI- Complete Edition v1.05
description: A mysterious illness suddenly broke out in girls in their teens and twenties, enhancing them mentally and granting them the ability to change their bodies into highly lethal weapons. The cause of the illness was a virus, currently classified into two types: the A-Virus and V-Virus.The world government enacted a law to care for patients infected with the Virus.
